@startuml
title BP-28 - Notification Reconciliation and Financial Reporting

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Platform|
start
:Collect payment orders, allocations, obligations and ledger entries;
:Prepare financial summaries;

|Notification Engine|
if (Notification event exists?) then (Yes)
  :Send payment or billing notification;
else (No)
  :Skip notification;
endif

|Finance Officer|
:Open reporting dashboard;
:Filter by tenant, date, product or payment method;

|Platform|
:Calculate outstanding bill report;
:Calculate collection report;
:Calculate revenue report;
:Calculate payment method report;
:Calculate settlement or ledger report;

|Finance Officer|
:Review and reconcile report totals;

if (Mismatch found?) then (Yes)
  :Investigate payment order and ledger details;
  :Export or escalate reconciliation issue;
else (No)
  :Confirm report is consistent;
endif

stop

note right
Current MVP has ledger listing and payment history basis.
Notification engine and full dashboard are future scope.
end note
@enduml
